---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="제품소개 | 케이비(주) KB Inc. — 에어서스펜션·액슬·유압실린더"
  description="VDL Weweler 에어서스펜션(MBS-HD 12T·GF·Lite S), VALX 드럼·디스크 액슬 상세 스펙, HS Penta 유압실린더(Light·Heavy·Front Mount)."
  active="products"
>
  <!-- PAGE HEADER + SUBNAV -->
  <section class="border-b border-hairline-steel relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-graphite-surface opacity-40 -skew-x-12 translate-x-1/3 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter pt-20 pb-10" data-reveal>
      <p class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-8 h-px bg-arterial-red"></span>제품소개 / PRODUCTS</p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest text-[clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.6rem)] leading-[1.1]">
        <span data-ko-only>특장차 3대 핵심 부품</span><span data-en-only>Three core components</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted-zinc text-lg mt-5 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        <span data-ko-only>에어서스펜션 · 액슬 · 유압실린더 — 유럽·미국 최고 브랜드의 검증된 제품군.</span>
        <span data-en-only>Air suspension · axles · hydraulic cylinders — proven ranges from Europe and America's leading brands.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter pb-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3 font-mono text-[13px]">
      <a href="#suspension" class="px-4 py-2 border border-hairline-steel text-muted-zinc hover:border-arterial-red hover:text-bright-alloy transition-colors">에어서스펜션</a>
      <a href="#axle" class="px-4 py-2 border border-hairline-steel text-muted-zinc hover:border-arterial-red hover:text-bright-alloy transition-colors">액슬</a>
      <a href="#cylinder" class="px-4 py-2 border border-hairline-steel text-muted-zinc hover:border-arterial-red hover:text-bright-alloy transition-colors">유압실린더</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 01 SUSPENSION -->
  <section id="suspension" class="border-b border-hairline-steel scroll-mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-section-v">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 border-l border-hairline-steel pl-8" data-reveal>
          <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">01 / AIR SUSPENSION · VDL WEWELER</span>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.6rem)] text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest"><span data-ko-only>에어서스펜션</span><span data-en-only>Air Suspension</span></h2>
          <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed max-w-md">
            <span data-ko-only>90여 년 역사의 네덜란드 VDL Weweler. 유럽 시장 점유율 30% 이상, 완전 자동화된 최신 생산시설에서 생산되어 전 세계 모든 대륙에 수출·사용되고 있습니다.</span>
            <span data-en-only>Netherlands-based VDL Weweler, with 90+ years of history and a 30%+ European market share, produced in fully automated facilities and exported across every continent.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 render-stage border border-hairline-steel bg-graphite-surface p-8 flex items-center justify-center" data-reveal-x>
          <img src="/assets/img/mbs_hd_12t.gif" alt="VDL Weweler 에어서스펜션" class="w-full max-h-[340px] object-contain" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-hairline-steel border border-hairline-steel" data-reveal>
        <div class="bg-charcoal-void p-7 flex flex-col gap-5">
          <div class="render-stage h-32 flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/assets/img/mbs_hd_12t.gif" alt="MBS-HD 12T" class="max-h-28 object-contain" /></div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between border-b border-hairline-steel pb-3">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-bright-alloy">MBS-HD 12T</h3>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-arterial-red">12 T</span>
          </div>
          <dl class="font-mono text-[12.5px] flex flex-col gap-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>최대하중</span><span data-en-only>Max load</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">12 톤</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>트레일링암</span><span data-en-only>Trailing arm</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">100×59mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>라이드하이트</span><span data-en-only>Ride height</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">385–575mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>에어스프링</span><span data-en-only>Air spring</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">Ø350mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>옵셋</span><span data-en-only>Offset</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">30/50/95mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>중량</span><span data-en-only>Weight</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">185–210kg</dd></div>
          </dl>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-charcoal-void p-7 flex flex-col gap-5">
          <div class="render-stage h-32 flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/assets/img/mbs_gf.gif" alt="MBS-GF" class="max-h-28 object-contain" /></div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between border-b border-hairline-steel pb-3">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-bright-alloy">MBS-GF</h3>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-arterial-red">9 T</span>
          </div>
          <dl class="font-mono text-[12.5px] flex flex-col gap-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>최대하중</span><span data-en-only>Max load</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">9 톤</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>트레일링암</span><span data-en-only>Trailing arm</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right"><span data-ko-only>단조</span><span data-en-only>Forged</span></dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>액슬</span><span data-en-only>Axle</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">Ø146mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>라이드하이트</span><span data-en-only>Ride height</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">310–460mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>에어스프링</span><span data-en-only>Air spring</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">Ø300/335mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>중량</span><span data-en-only>Weight</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">128–150kg</dd></div>
          </dl>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-charcoal-void p-7 flex flex-col gap-5">
          <div class="render-stage h-32 flex items-center justify-center"><img src="/assets/img/mbs_lite_s.gif" alt="MBS-Lite S" class="max-h-28 object-contain" /></div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between border-b border-hairline-steel pb-3">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-bright-alloy">MBS-Lite S</h3>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-arterial-red">9 / 10 T</span>
          </div>
          <dl class="font-mono text-[12.5px] flex flex-col gap-2">
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>최대하중</span><span data-en-only>Max load</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">9 / 10 톤</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>트레일링암</span><span data-en-only>Trailing arm</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">95×49mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>라이드하이트</span><span data-en-only>Ride height</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">240–540mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>에어스프링</span><span data-en-only>Air spring</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">Ø330/335mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>옵셋</span><span data-en-only>Offset</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">20/50mm</dd></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-4"><dt class="text-muted-zinc"><span data-ko-only>중량</span><span data-en-only>Weight</span></dt><dd class="text-bright-alloy text-right">135–155kg</dd></div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 font-mono text-[13px] text-muted-zinc" data-reveal>
        <img src="/assets/img/axle_lift.gif" alt="Axle Lift" class="h-12 w-auto opacity-80" />
        <p><span class="text-bright-alloy"><span data-ko-only>볼트온 액슬리프트</span><span data-en-only>Bolt-on axle lift</span></span> — AL-456 (<span data-ko-only>드럼</span><span data-en-only>drum</span>) / AL-457 (<span data-ko-only>디스크</span><span data-en-only>disc</span>)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 02 AXLE -->
  <section id="axle" class="border-b border-hairline-steel scroll-mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-section-v">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 render-stage border border-hairline-steel bg-graphite-surface p-8 flex items-center justify-center" data-reveal-x>
          <img src="/assets/img/valx_disc500.gif" alt="VALX 액슬" class="w-full max-h-[200px] object-contain" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 border-l border-hairline-steel pl-8" data-reveal>
          <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">02 / AXLES · VALX</span>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.6rem)] text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest"><span data-ko-only>액슬</span><span data-en-only>Axles</span></h2>
          <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed max-w-md">
            <span data-ko-only>유럽 최고 기술로 설계·제작된 네덜란드 VALX 액슬. 드럼 브레이크는 Textar, 디스크는 WABCO, 씰은 SKF, 메인베어링은 TIMKEN 등 각 부품의 세계적 브랜드를 채택했습니다.</span>
            <span data-en-only>VALX axles engineered in the Netherlands — Textar for drum brakes, WABCO for disc, SKF seals, and TIMKEN main bearings.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-14" data-reveal>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4"><img src="/assets/img/valx_drum100.gif" alt="drum" class="h-12 w-auto" /><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-bright-alloy">VALX Drum Brake Axles</h3></div>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="spec-table min-w-[560px]">
            <thead><tr><th><span data-ko-only>항목</span><span data-en-only>Spec</span></th><th class="is-featured">DRUM 420</th><th>DRUM 360</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><th>Axle load</th><td>9000 kg</td><td>9000 kg</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Wheel size</th><td>22.5"</td><td>19.5"</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Axle beam</th><td>Ø146×10</td><td>Ø146×10</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Hub offset</th><td>0 mm</td><td>0 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Wheel bolts</th><td>10 ~ M22×1.5</td><td>8–10 ~ M22×1.5</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Bolt circle</th><td>335 mm</td><td>275 / 335 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Brake</th><td>VALX Drum</td><td>VALX Drum</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Brake dim.</th><td>420×180 mm</td><td>360×200 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Bearings</th><td>Timken B-145662~B-145649</td><td>Timken B-145662~B-145649</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Seal</th><td>SKF 4 lip</td><td>SKF 4 lip</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Air suspension</th><td>Weweler MBS</td><td>Weweler MBS</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Ride height</th><td>210–420 mm</td><td>210–420 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Air spring Ø</th><td>300 / 335 mm</td><td>300 / 335 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Air spring offset</th><td>0/25/50/65/90 mm</td><td>0/25/50/65/90 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Axle lift</th><td>Optional</td><td>Optional</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4"><img src="/assets/img/valx_disc100.gif" alt="disc" class="h-12 w-auto" /><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-bright-alloy">VALX Disc Brake Axles</h3></div>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="spec-table min-w-[560px]">
            <thead><tr><th><span data-ko-only>항목</span><span data-en-only>Spec</span></th><th class="is-featured">DISK 430</th><th>DISK 370</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><th>Axle load</th><td>9000 kg</td><td>9000 kg</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Wheel size</th><td>22.5"</td><td>19.5" / 22.5"</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Axle beam</th><td>Ø146×10</td><td>Ø146×10</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Hub offset</th><td>120 / 0 mm</td><td>120 / 0 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Wheel bolts</th><td>10 ~ M22×1.5</td><td>10 ~ M22×1.5</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Bolt circle</th><td>335 mm</td><td>335 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Brake</th><td>Wabco</td><td>Wabco</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Brake dim.</th><td>Pan 22-1</td><td>Pan 19-1</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Bearings</th><td>Timken B-145662~B-145649</td><td>Timken B-145662~B-145649</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Seal</th><td>SKF 4 lip</td><td>SKF 4 lip</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Ride height</th><td>210–420 mm</td><td>210–420 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Air spring Ø</th><td>300 / 335 mm</td><td>300 / 335 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>L1 / L2</th><td>520 / 320 mm</td><td>520 / 320 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Air spring offset</th><td>0/25/50/65/90 mm</td><td>0/25/50/65/90 mm</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Axle lift</th><td>Optional</td><td>Optional</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 03 CYLINDER -->
  <section id="cylinder" class="border-b border-hairline-steel scroll-mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-section-v">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 flex flex-col items-start gap-5 border-l border-hairline-steel pl-8" data-reveal>
          <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">03 / HYDRAULIC CYLINDERS · HS PENTA</span>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.6rem)] text-bright-alloy tracking-tightest"><span data-ko-only>유압실린더</span><span data-en-only>Hydraulic Cylinders</span></h2>
          <p class="text-muted-zinc leading-relaxed max-w-md">
            <span data-ko-only>이탈리아 HS Penta(Inter Pump Group). 용접 없이 통 강관 내·외경을 직접 가공하고 도금 피스톤로드를 표준 채택하여 수명을 연장한 고강성 다단 실린더입니다.</span>
            <span data-en-only>Italy's HS Penta (Inter Pump Group). Seamless tubes machined inside and out — no welds — with plated piston rods as standard for extended service life.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 render-stage border border-hairline-steel bg-graphite-surface p-8 flex items-center justify-center" data-reveal-x>
          <img src="/assets/img/penta_cylinders200.png" alt="HS Penta 유압실린더" class="w-full max-h-[320px] object-contain" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-hairline-steel border border-hairline-steel" data-reveal>
        <div class="bg-charcoal-void p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">LIGHT DUTY</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-bright-alloy"><span data-ko-only>라이트 듀티</span><span data-en-only>Light Duty</span></h3>
          <ul class="text-muted-zinc text-[14px] leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-2 list-none">
            <li><span data-ko-only>이음매 없는 열간 단조 파이프 내·외경 가공</span><span data-en-only>Seamless hot-forged pipe, machined inside &amp; out</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>넓은 중첩구간으로 지지강도 확보</span><span data-en-only>Wide overlap for added support strength</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>용접 없는 통파이프 · 최대 220bar</span><span data-en-only>Weld-free tube · up to 220 bar</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>도금 피스톤로드 표준 채택</span><span data-en-only>Plated piston rod as standard</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-arterial-red border-t border-hairline-steel pt-3 mt-auto">10 ~ 20 <span class="text-muted-zinc">톤</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-charcoal-void p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">HEAVY DUTY</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-bright-alloy"><span data-ko-only>헤비 듀티</span><span data-en-only>Heavy Duty</span></h3>
          <ul class="text-muted-zinc text-[14px] leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-2 list-none">
            <li><span data-ko-only>열간단조강관 내·외경 + 호닝 가공</span><span data-en-only>Hot-forged tube, machined + honed</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>이중 탑가이드로 우수한 지지강도</span><span data-en-only>Twin top guides for superior support</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>동급 대비 탁월한 티핑 능력</span><span data-en-only>Outstanding tipping capacity in its class</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>최대 스트로크 6,500mm</span><span data-en-only>Max stroke 6,500 mm</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-arterial-red border-t border-hairline-steel pt-3 mt-auto">4 ~ 62 <span class="text-muted-zinc">톤</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-charcoal-void p-7 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-mono text-[13px] text-arterial-red">FRONT MOUNT</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-bright-alloy"><span data-ko-only>프론트 마운트</span><span data-en-only>Front Mount</span></h3>
          <ul class="text-muted-zinc text-[14px] leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-2 list-none">
            <li><span data-ko-only>이음매 없는 열간 단조 파이프 가공</span><span data-en-only>Seamless hot-forged pipe machining</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>용접 없는 통 강관 고압 작동</span><span data-en-only>Weld-free tube, high-pressure operation</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>우수한 강도와 정밀 가공</span><span data-en-only>Excellent strength, precision machining</span></li>
            <li><span data-ko-only>최대 스트로크 10,500mm</span><span data-en-only>Max stroke 10,500 mm</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-arterial-red border-t border-hairline-steel pt-3 mt-auto">20 ~ 100 <span class="text-muted-zinc">톤</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-arterial-red">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-gutter py-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
